{{Quote|Anybody who makes it down the Rampa Rapids with a load of fresh water these days is a rich man.|[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]|<ref name="Han Solo's Revenge">''[[Han Solo's Revenge]]''</ref>}}
'''Rampa Rapids''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace trade route]] that linked [[R'alla]] to [[Rampa III]].

==History==
{{Quote|Last I heard, you two took some fire on the Rampa Rapids.|[[Sonniod/Legends|Sonniod]] to Han Solo|<ref name="Han Solo's Revenge" />}}
This route was used by [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] to supply [[Rampa III]] in water from nearby [[R'alla]]. It was strictly controlled by [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] [[Gunship/Legends|gunships]]<ref name="TEA" /> of the [[Rampa Skywatch]].<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|III|77|Rampa}}</ref>

Smuggler [[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]] found falsified cargo manifests for a run down the Rampa Rapids once while cleaning out the computer files of the ship.<ref name="SL5">{{JournalCite|5|Smuggler's Log}}</ref> [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] and [[Reck Desh]] once transported [[R'alla mineral water/Legends|R'alla mineral water]] to Rampa III.<ref name="AoC1">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref>

